title: Application for filming and photography in the libraries: Libraries - Northwestern University
content: Please fill out the form below to apply for any filming or photography within the libraries. Please allow at least 5 business days between your request and your filming/photography date for a response. Priority for library spaces is given to requestsÂ  that further the Libraries mission of supporting teaching, learning, and research. Academic and student requests will be given preference, based on available space, time of year, possible disruptions, and available staff.
